data.name: Asspixel (revived)
data.description:
# Server Info
This is a revival of the original Asspixel. The server is online infrequently. The only available gamemode right now is BedWars.
All your data from Asspixel is also available here.
**OneblockX is not available.**

---

## Old description
Originally founded, developed and ran by FrenchToast. Asspixel is a Hypixel-like alternative for Eaglercraft. We make as good of an experience as we possibly can for our players.
